hristendom to demonstrate and even \\\"push\\\" LGBTQ+ diversity?\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.198591588435153e-13, \"text\": \"Christendom\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most sacred rites\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"depictions\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+ diversity\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously not.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And \\\"we did not intend that\\\" does not justify such clear offensive oversight.\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such clear offensive oversight\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the secular world can refrain from displaying images of Mohammed because Islam condemns them, can it not offer respect without defaming Jesus and offending Christians around the world?\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.999995979098356, \"rank\": 4.020918037494369e-06, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9913013740868247, \"rank\": 0.008774955796869885, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the secular world\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"images\", \"from\": 1834