iniscule to the majority) will have to be handled on a case-by-case basis.\", \"from\": 10693, \"to\": 10996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10795, \"end\": 10797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999912122215894, \"rank\": 8.787855442871063e-06, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a general rule\", \"from\": 10696, \"to\": 10710}, {\"ngram\": \"provenXY chromosomesfight\", \"from\": 10727, \"to\": 10752}, {\"ngram\": \"male competitions\", \"from\": 10756, \"to\": 10773}, {\"ngram\": \"female competitions\", \"from\": 10819, \"to\": 10838}, {\"ngram\": \"evenintersex individualsoftenlean\", \"from\": 10840, \"to\": 10873}, {\"ngram\": \"Variance\", \"from\": 10895, \"to\": 10903}, {\"ngram\": \"these(however\", \"from\": 10907, \"to\": 10920}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 10934, \"to\": 10946}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 10985, \"to\": 10989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EvenReem Alsalem, the U.N.'s special rapporteur on violence against women and girls, echoed the need for further gender testing of some type: \\\"We know that there are simple, efficient, dignified ways of testing sex \\u2026 that are not invasive, that are cheap and that are reliable.\", \"from\": 10998, \"to\": 11275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11020, \"end\": 11024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.156372240954869e-19, \"text\": \"U.N.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"EvenReem Alsalem\", \"from\": 10998, \"to\": 11014}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 11049, \"to\": 11057}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 11066, \"to\": 11071}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 1